{"tid":1494583,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"<人手置頂>香港人你已經被監視 824觀塘遊行五大訴求 ,反監控!","createTime":"2019-08-21T16:42:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T04:08:28.000Z","uid":211707,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"683b2aa3b1d12775c8d9c3c67f2608853e386e5f","tid":1494583,"uid":211707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T16:42:38.000Z","msg":"(代po)<br />\n<br />\n<strong>各位巴絲全民被監控，已經殺到埋身！</strong><br />\n全港短期內將有 400 支監控燈柱，5,200 個鏡頭。全部燈柱及大部份鏡頭都有 人面識別功能， 藍牙傳送器，RFID 追蹤技術。 <br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1298190\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1298190</a><br />\n<strong><ins>睇片</ins></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/AntiCCTV/videos/539040930169165\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FAntiCCTV%2Fvideos%2F539040930169165&d=qWTZpUodHfCf2bB0mbfn08bSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=18f38d53\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/AntiCCTV/videos/539040930169165</a><br />\n<br />\n狗鐵cctv 直通警總， 狗鐵大量加建人面識別cctv。<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1493130\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1493130</a>  <br />\n<br />\n 你覺得你可以獨善其身咩？ <strong>今日新疆，明日香港！</strong>如果我哋再唔企出黎， 香港可能會有再教育營 所有去過遊行嘅香港人， 都要再受教育，你到時走得甩咩？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1433939\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1433939</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong> 全面監控等於直接送中！</strong> 到時我地連遊行自由都冇， 香港將會面目全非！<br />\n黑警濫捕打到我哋30個手足要瞓醫院， 我哋 一定要為佢哋行出嚟, 以眼還眼<br />\n<br />\n<strong>觀塘遊行路線</strong><br />\n*駿業街遊樂場行到零碳天地， 13:00集合，13:30起步。 * <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求缺一不可!<br />\n反監控！<br />\n追究黑警濫用暴力！<br />\n824 和理優， 觀塘見<br />\n不反對通知書申請中<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FzjCGwZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFzjCGwZ.jpg&h=cde3b471&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4Hu3B5m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4Hu3B5m.jpg&h=b82c0122&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JBqyeR2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJBqyeR2.jpg&h=8de3ee7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TvqZaqv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTvqZaqv.jpg&h=e7343bf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BUOjUSb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBUOjUSb.jpg&h=976c72a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tOaN3Ly.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtOaN3Ly.jpg&h=03349d05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sr1YqYU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsr1YqYU.jpg&h=4fdb966a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NF9bLY0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNF9bLY0.png&h=e1eb30d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jhzGoO8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjhzGoO8.jpg&h=19455643&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qaYoB89.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqaYoB89.jpg&h=06611a52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cy9rzVQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcy9rzVQ.jpg&h=ce025114&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6ApK52B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6ApK52B.jpg&h=52378813&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"846dec0c02aff300e89eef2fe94616f368e478b3","tid":1494583,"uid":211707,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T16:47:15.000Z","msg":"824 觀塘見"},{"pid":"95c7527e7c69c08abaec795da5a922d5c1381369","tid":1494583,"uid":211707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T16:50:42.000Z","msg":"十連推"},{"pid":"18f95bf13dc52464f8730e8053db3d176d80a04d","tid":1494583,"uid":211707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite